WEBVTT

00:00.360 --> 00:00.920
Kill

00:25.400 --> 00:26.120
What a pity

00:26.120 --> 00:27.960
Prince of Jin was defeated and ordered to die

00:28.200 --> 00:30.720
The Chen family's eldest daughter jumped from a building to follow

00:31.000 --> 00:32.720
Such deep devotion

00:32.720 --> 00:34.200
Even if the realm is lost

00:34.200 --> 00:36.680
Cannot help but break one's heart

00:37.200 --> 00:38.000
As the saying goes

00:38.240 --> 00:39.720
Easy to find priceless treasures

00:39.720 --> 00:41.240
Hard to find a devoted lover

00:41.720 --> 00:43.560
Pitiful pair of devoted lovers

00:43.640 --> 00:46.360
Finally became ill-fated lovers
